tutorial.account_text1:
1. You can log in by clicking on the 'login' button at the top right corner of the platform. **[1]**
2. If you have not yet created an account, you will need to first register. **[2]**
3. Once you are logged in, you will see your name appear in the top right corner of the site, in a yellow box. Click on the box to open 'Account & settings' **[3]**
4. You have now reached 'My profile' page. **[4]** It provides information about
    1. Your name;
    2. Your email address;
    3. How to change your password
    4. When you signed up;
    5. Last time you updated your profile;
    6. How many times you have logged in on the platform;
    7. Your last login date.
5. This is also where you can: Select your preferred language or decide to see the tutorial on login.

