Data privacy and security is core to the collaboration between Flowminder and Digicel Haiti. For information on how data are collected, processed and protected, we recommend you read the following two pages:
1. [Our Website privacy notice](/privacy) describing how we protect the privacy of the visitors on this platform;
2. [Subscribers data privacy page](/subscribers-privacy), describing how we protect the privacy of Digicel Haiti's subscribers.
